Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.95,0:23:00.69,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Petit Clover!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.06,0:23:05.02,sign_33188_278_The_Mystery_of_t,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(520,1}Splitting Up
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.26,0:23:03.94,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Splitting Up.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.03,0:23:09.42,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Asta, are you sure you want to split \Nup and go off on your own?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.42,0:23:12.21,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mock me! Of course \NI'm fine with that!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.21,0:23:13.54,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Are you absolutely positive?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.54,0:23:14.37,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.37,0:23:17.91,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I'll ask you just one more time. \NAre you sure you're okay with splitting up?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.91,0:23:20.06,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I said yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.06,0:23:23.51,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What? Are you gonna be lonely, Yuno?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.51,0:23:24.54,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,You can't be serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.54,0:23:26.93,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's split up, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.93,0:23:28.31,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,See you at the royal capital!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.31,0:23:29.30,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.02,0:23:31.82,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,See ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.82,0:23:32.64,main,Digit,0000,0000,0000,,So mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.89,0:23:37.93,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.67,0:23:36.85,main,Digit,0000,0000,0000,,So mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.78,0:23:41.77,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,I came because I heard \Nthe town was being attacked!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.77,0:23:43.84,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell, Luck?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.84,0:23:44.64,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.64,0:23:46.90,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Why the hell are you attacking me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.33,0:23:51.22,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on {\i1}Black Clover{\i0}, Page 104: \N"Lightning of Rage vs. Friends."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.07,0:23:54.25,sign_34238_338_Page_2_The_Boys_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(234,1)}Page 104\N\N{\fs18} Lightning of Rage vs. Friends
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.22,0:23:54.07,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Vanessa! We're taking Luck back!
